<section xml:id="restarting-the-ite" version="5.0" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
                                               xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                                               xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" >
  <title>Restarting the ITE</title>
  <para>
    You can restart the ITE with the current workspace using:
  </para>
  
  <para>
    <emphasis role="menuPath">File</emphasis>--&gt;<emphasis role="menuPath">Restart</emphasis>
  </para>
  <para>
    You can also restart the ITE with a new workspace by selecting:
  </para>
  
  <para>
    <emphasis role="menuPath">File</emphasis>--&gt;<emphasis role="menuPath">Switch Workspace</emphasis>
  </para>
</section>